{"body": "To break your tests, you can just add:\r\n\r\n    attr_protected :pirate_id\r\n\r\nto `test/models/bird.rb`. It shouldn't work like that, should it? The bug with merging `creation_attributes` was hidden, until the \"strict\" mass assignment sanitizer was introduced. It definitely can't be fixed like that, you can create a separate issue for that (with a reference to the previous one, etc.).", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/3240964", "created_at": "2011-12-21T22:57:42Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/4122#issuecomment-3240964", "updated_at": "2011-12-21T22:57:42Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 4122, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/qoobaa/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/qoobaa/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/qoobaa/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/qoobaa", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/qoobaa/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/qoobaa", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/qoobaa/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/48acd2a1c5c447f7e7b59310ee1fecff?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Ff2b4053221961416d47d497814a8064f.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/qoobaa/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/qoobaa/received_events", "gravatar_id": "48acd2a1c5c447f7e7b59310ee1fecff", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/qoobaa/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "qoobaa", "type": "User", "id": 10659, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/qoobaa/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "52382c44bd3543c15100f1c9"}, "id": 3240964, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/4122"}
